summary: An Ordinance authorizing and directing the City Comptroller to draw a warrant in favor of Thomas K. Ensminger, for the purpose of purchasing a certain tract, piece or parcel of land in the North Half of the Southeast Quarter of the Northeast Quarter (N 1/2 of SE 1/4 of NE 1/4) of Section Five (5), Township Twenty-five (25) north, Range Four (4) East, W. M., and appropriating money therefor.
